1.  Install Node JS. Basic Installation.
2.  On Command Prompt:
--------------------------
Install Ionic                               -           npm install -g ionic
Make a directory for Ionic Projects         -           mkdir Ionic

Start Ionic Project -     cd Ionic  (cmd, Navigate to project folder)
                          ionic start   (cmd)
                          Give a project name
                          choose a template (navigate using TAB)
                          ionic server  (cmd, start the application)
                          
                          
                          
                          
